  - don't handle other window interaction yet
  - URLs must always be in the form db#file
    - if no db name is present assume ${window.DB}
    - if no # hash symbol is present, assume the whole thing is a hash
  - example: if DB='main' then #chat should map to main#chat
  - example: if DB='apps/paint' and file is 'art/selfie' then it should map to apps/paint#art/selfie
